{
  "stem": "20686.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father was a universalist, and he believed in brotherhood, and that tomorrow-- after tomorrow, this modern Messiah will come, and-- and we'll be having new life, and brotherhood which will-- utopian.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It-- I-- I believe-- it's my belief that most of Jewish Bundists, their whole political attitude was rather it came-- came a-- a-- a new understanding of humanism.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think it was-- it was in a sense an Erasmian attitude to a new society, not the-- the Bolshevik, and not the Communist, not even the sort of a-- I-- I really can't-- this is-- this is something which most probably was part of the-- the horizon, an Erasmian society, a humanistic society, where people will be able to live in peace with one another.",
      "word_count": 66
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there will be this eternal brotherhood, which was also prophesized by the prophets, by Jeremiahs and Isaiahs, and-- and all of-- Amoses, all those.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This was there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I-- I think that it actually was the old philosophy in a new form.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The same thing I believe.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I never told [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the people I came in contact anything about comrade.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this in itself is not just a-- a name, something you say.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a concept, comrade.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Like we talked about, when I was a boy, we talked about the French Social Democratic Party, about Leon Blum, who knew about me as much as I knew-- as I knew about the moon.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I called him chaver Leon Blum, comrade Leon Blum.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I remember during the Austrian uprising in Schutzbund, uprised against the-- the fascist system in Austria.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There were people like leaders, Koloman Wallisch, Julius Deutsch, [?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Munichreiter, ?] [? and Weissel. ?] I always called them comrade.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
